@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### 1) 단건 답안 제출 (학생 9001, 문항 2001) - 첫 제출
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/exams/1001/answers
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: 9001

{
  "questionId": 2001,
  "answerText": "TCP"
}

### 2) 단건 답안 제출 (학생 9001, 문항 2002) - 다음 문항
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/exams/1001/answers
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: 9001

{
  "questionId": 2002,
  "answerText": "4"
}

### 3) 진행 현황 조회 (전체)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/exams/1001/progress

### 4) 진행 현황 조회 (since 지정: 1시간 전 epoch milli 예시)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/exams/1001/progress?since=1719990000000

### 5) 교사용 상세 조회 (학생 9001)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/exams/1001/students/9001
